   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Water - Donate This Gift to 170 Kids in Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The biggest issue in Africa is the inability to find fresh, clean water for drinking and daily living. Most people in Africa rely on surface water and don&apos;t have the technology or the money to dig wells to harvest groundwater. The mission of Smile for Africa foundation is to make the small donations add up to a big change. With our current project we will help Greenfield Kids Foundation in Kabale, Uganda and will support 170 students to have clean water.</narrative>
  </description>
